  {
    "type": "Bug",
    "conclusion": "为TopologyManager添加CPU-attached NUMA过滤选项，优化大NUMA系统性能。",
    "description": "在`projectToEffectiveNUMANodes`方法中，当`effectiveNodeID`超出`distances`切片索引范围时，代码会跳过该节点。然而，如果所有`effectiveNodeID`都越界，`closestNodes`将保持为空，导致后续`len(closestNodes) == 0`条件成立，并错误地将所有`m.numaNodes`插入`projected`集合。这可能导致设备拓扑提示被错误地投影到所有NUMA节点，而不是最近的节点，从而影响拓扑对齐的准确性。",
    "evidence": "文件: pkg/kubelet/cm/devicemanager/manager.go
@@ -187,6 +201,54 @@ func (m *ManagerImpl) Updates() <-chan resourceupdates.Update {
 	return m.update
 }

+func (m *ManagerImpl) projectToEffectiveNUMANodes(rawNUMANodes []int) []int {
+	if len(rawNUMANodes) == 0 {
+		return nil
+	}
+	if len(m.numaNodes) == 0 {
+		return rawNUMANodes
+	}
+
+	effectiveNUMANodes := sets.New[int](m.numaNodes...)
+	projected := sets.New[int]()
+	for _, nodeID := range rawNUMANodes {
+		if effectiveNUMANodes.Has(nodeID) {
+			projected.Insert(nodeID)
+			continue
+		}
+
+		distances, ok := m.numaDistances[nodeID]
+		if !ok || len(distances) == 0 {
+			projected.Insert(m.numaNodes...)
+			continue
+		}
+
+		minDistance := uint64(math.MaxUint64)
+		closestNodes := make([]int, 0, len(m.numaNodes))
+		for _, effectiveNodeID := range m.numaNodes {
+			if effectiveNodeID < 0 || effectiveNodeID >= len(distances) {
+				continue
+			}
+			distance := distances[effectiveNodeID]
+			if distance < minDistance {
+				minDistance = distance
+				closestNodes = []int{effectiveNodeID}
+				continue
+			}
+			if distance == minDistance {
+				closestNodes = append(closestNodes, effectiveNodeID)
+			}
+		}
+		if len(closestNodes) == 0 {
+			projected.Insert(m.numaNodes...)
+			continue
+		}
+		projected.Insert(closestNodes...)
+	}
+
+	return sets.List(projected)
+}",
    "advice": "建议在内部循环开始前，初始化一个`foundClosest`标志。如果所有`effectiveNodeID`都因索引越界而被跳过，应视为距离数据无效，并回退到将`m.numaNodes`全部插入的逻辑（类似于`!ok || len(distances) == 0`的情况）。或者，更稳健的做法是确保`numaDistances`的数据结构与系统报告的NUMA节点ID完全匹配，并在初始化时进行验证。",
    "confidence": 0.8,
    "severity": "Medium"
  },
  {
    "type": "Readability",
    "conclusion": "为TopologyManager添加CPU-attached NUMA过滤选项，优化大NUMA系统性能。",
    "description": "在`getNUMANodesForTopologyHints`方法中，使用`map[int]struct{}`来创建集合并进行交集操作，代码略显冗长且效率不高。Kubernetes项目中广泛使用`sets.Set[T]`类型来处理集合操作，此处可以改用`sets.Set[int]`来简化代码，提高可读性和一致性。",
    "evidence": "文件: pkg/kubelet/cm/memorymanager/policy_static.go
@@ -979,6 +978,37 @@ func (p *staticPolicy) calculateHints(machineState state.NUMANodeMap, pod *v1.Po
